lyrics:
[Verse]
In a world of blocks, we start anew
With dreams of adventure, and treasures too
We'll gather materials, day and night
Digging and crafting, in the pale moonlight

[Chorus]
On this Minecraft survival journey we roam
Facing each challenge, together we'll grow
From the humble beginnings, to the great unknown
We'll conquer the world, till the dragon is overthrown
